---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Contact Us | Word Hunt Solver"
  description="Have feedback, found a bug, or need help with the word hunt solver? Reach out and we will respond fast."
  path="/contact"
>
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-10 sm:py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-brand-700 dark:text-white sm:text-4xl">Contact Us</h1>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Get In Touch</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm">
      Found a bug in the word hunt solver, or have an idea to make it better? We would love to hear from
      you.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Contact Form</h2>
    <form class="card mt-4 space-y-4">
      <div>
        <label class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm" for="name">Name</label>
        <input id="name" name="name" type="text" class="mt-1 w-full rounded-lg border border-brand-100 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-brand-900 dark:border-brand-700 dark:bg-brand-900 dark:text-white" />
      </div>
      <div>
        <label class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm" for="email">Email</label>
        <input id="email" name="email" type="email" class="mt-1 w-full rounded-lg border border-brand-100 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-brand-900 dark:border-brand-700 dark:bg-brand-900 dark:text-white" />
      </div>
      <div>
        <label class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm" for="message">Message</label>
        <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="4" class="mt-1 w-full rounded-lg border border-brand-100 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-brand-900 dark:border-brand-700 dark:bg-brand-900 dark:text-white"></textarea>
      </div>
      <button type="submit" class="btn-accent">Send Message</button>
      <p class="text-xs text-brand-400">[This form still needs to be wired to a real backend or form service, e.g. Formspree, before it can actually send messages. Right now it will not submit anywhere.]</p>
    </form>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Email Us Directly</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm">
      Prefer email? Reach us directly at
      <a href="mailto:wordhuntsolvers@gmail.com" class="anchor-link">wordhuntsolvers@gmail.com</a>.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Report a Bug or Missing Word</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm">
      If the solver missed a valid word or showed one that should not count, tell us the board and the word
      so we can check our dictionary.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Response Time</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm">We aim to reply within 24 to 48 hours.</p>
  </article>
</Layout>
